### Technical Framework

- **Core Stack**: Python 3.8+, PyGithub, GitPython, OpenAI/Anthropic
- **Key Libraries**: PyYAML, Jinja2, Click, Twine, Build
- **Build System**: setuptools with pyproject.toml
- **Testing**: pytest with coverage

